864, 176.4558, 176.5139, 177.0542, 178.9841, 178.2275, 177.5438, 178.4578, 179.9177, 181.6628, 187.5048, 191.2708, 189.9959, 189.9047, 188.2589, 190.2354, 188.9804, 189.4709, 188.8697, 187.9184, 187.0954, 187.7257, 187.6928, 186.6271, 187.4297, 186.6655, 187.5527, 189.1859, 188.9806, 188.3663, 188.3637, 187.2626, 186.9959, 187.07, 189.5141, 189.7105, 189.5429, 190.6699, 188.8416, 189.5565, 189.3434, 190.5215, 191.1616, 190.4551, 190.7756, 191.1176, 191.4129, 191.776, 191.9454, 190.8154, 193.2098, 192.9048, 195.9161, 195.3339, 195.8635, 198.1527, 198.5165, 200.0595, 197.4965, 194.6562, 194.8842, 192.7662, 194.0071, 195.4575, 194.0186, 193.7281, 193.8057, 194.245, 195.2518, 193.7165, 193.8105, 194.8388, 193.8623, 192.1184, 191.7536, 191.511, 194.0777, 195.8159, 197.2892, 197.4342, 196.6104, 196.8445, 199.4361, 199.6598, 198.6505, 197.9858, 200.625, 202.1009, 202.9711, 205.6842, 202.2211, 200.2233, 199.6378, 198.8538, 199.3352, 200.359, 199.3354, 199.2586, 199.4192, 201.1427, 200.0408, 198.3117, 198.6105, 199.1642, 199.5182, 200.6801, 200.427, 199.9909, 199.6374, 196.4379, 199.0219, 199.5068, 199.2636, 199.5592, 200.3692, 200.3668, 201.3797, 199.9047, 200.2337, 199.6185, 198.0662, 197.1206], "summary_html": "<h1>Weekly Momentum in Commodity Futures -- Factor Summary</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>论文发现商品期货中存在显著的短期动量效应（weekly momentum），与股票市场的短期反转截然不同。论文将过去52周分解为4个不重叠子区间，发现1周动量（CMOM_{1,1}）是最强且最稳健的因子，无法被carry、股票动量或套保压力解释。</p>\n<p>在中国商品期货上复现时，<strong>年度动量</strong>（CMOM_{52,27}，即跳过近6个月、使用前6个月的回报率）表现最优，Sharpe达1.19。这可能反映了中国商品期货市场的微观结构差异——更长周期的动量信号在A股商品期货上更有效。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.04</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-13.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3190</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.12</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.34</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.22 / 1.05</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.01</td><td>1.34</td><td>1.09</td><td>0.22</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.63</span></td><td>0.75</td><td>0.47</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.0</span></td><td>0.29</td><td>0.87</td><td>0.82</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.24</span></td><td>1.71</td><td>0.52</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3192</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>40.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>16.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>论文定义四种动量信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{CMOM}_{k_1, k_2} = \\text{sort commodities by} \\sum_{t=t_0-k_1}^{t_0-k_2} r_{i,t}</div>\n<p>具体为：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{1,1}</span>: 过去1周收益（日频约5天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{4,2}</span>: 过去第2-4周收益（日频约6-20天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{26,5}</span>: 过去第5-26周收益（日频约21-130天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{52,27}</span>: 过去第27-52周收益（日频约131-260天）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>最优实现使用 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{52,27}</span>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i = \\frac{P_{i,t-130}}{P_{i,t-260}} - 1</div>\n<p>截面排名后取top 20% long、bottom 20% short，IC-gate过滤弱品种，vol-target缩放。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1</strong>: 实现论文4种动量子区间 + combo。结果：yearly_mom_252d_raw Sharpe 1.19 最强，weekly_mom_5d_raw Sharpe -0.15 最弱。与论文发现的\"weekly最强\"相反，中国商品市场上长期动量更有效。</li>\n<li><strong>R2</strong>: 扩展参数网格（lookback x hold_days），添加12-1经典动量。yr_mom_h10_raw Sharpe 1.08，未超过R1最优。</li>\n<li><strong>R3</strong>: 细化quintile阈值（15%/20%/30%）、连续信号、IC-gating。yr_q20_h5_ic_raw 达到Sharpe 1.19，与R1最优持平。决策=skip（通过）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（57个），黑色系（HC/JM/RB）和油脂（P）贡献最大</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每5天换仓，信号lookback 260天</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 年度Sharpe波动较大（2019/2021/2024偏低），说明长期动量在趋势不明确年份表现偏弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.3s</li>\n</ul>"}